Reasoning: The paper deals with object detection and classification in images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The proposed framework also involves Bayesian modeling and learning, which are key topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of language models for scene parsing suggests a connection to natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the evaluation of the proposed approach on a database of indoor scenes suggests a possible connection to robotics (cs.RO).
